<h1>指</h1><p class=neha><span style="color:#009900;">zhǐ</span><span class=alesi>(zhi3)</span> , <span style="color:#cc7700;">zhí</span><span class=alesi>(zhi2)</span> , <span style="color:#990000;">zhī</span><span class=alesi>(zhi1)</span> <span class=lesi>// pronunciations of 指 in Mandarin Pinyin</span></p><h2>Basic information about 指</h2><div class=abo>
<p><b>Unihan definition:</b> <a href="/dictionary/finger" style="color:black;">finger</a>, <a href="/dictionary/toe" style="color:black;">toe</a>; <a href="/dictionary/point" style="color:black;">point</a>, indicate</p><p><b>Number of strokes:</b> 9<br><small>Examples of other characters consisting of 9 strokes: <a href="/character/是" title="shi4: indeed, yes, right; to be; demonstrative pronoun, this, that">是</a>, <a href="/character/说" title="shuo1: speak, say, talk; scold, upbraid">说</a>, <a href="/character/要" title="yao4: necessary, essential; necessity">要</a>, <a href="/character/种" title="zhong3: seed; race, breed; to plant">种</a>, <a href="/character/面" title="mian4: face; surface; plane; side, dimension">面</a>, <a href="/character/看" title="kan4: look, see; examine, scrutinize">看</a>, <a href="/character/前" title="qian2: in front, forward; preceding">前</a>, <a href="/character/点" title="dian3: dot, speck, spot; point, degree">点</a>, <a href="/character/将" title="jiang1: will, going to, future; general">将</a>, <a href="/character/很" title="hen3: very, quite, much">很</a></small></p><p><b>Radical:</b> <a href="/character/手" title="Kangxi radical 64">手</a>&nbsp;64.6</p><p><b>HSK level:</b> 4 <br><small>Other HSK 4 characters: <a href="/character/克" title="ke4: gram; overcome; transliteration">克</a>, <a href="/character/金" title="jin1: gold; metals in general; money">金</a>, <a href="/character/许" title="xu3: allow, permit; promise; betroth">许</a>, <a href="/character/命" title="ming4: life; destiny, fate, luck; an order, instruction">命</a>, <a href="/character/区" title="qu1: area, district, region, ward">区</a>, <a href="/character/资" title="zi1: property; wealth; capital">资</a>, <a href="/character/保" title="bao3: protect, safeguard, defend, care">保</a>, <a href="/character/至" title="zhi4: reach, arrive; extremely, very">至</a>, <a href="/character/队" title="dui4: team, group; army unit">队</a>, <a href="/character/社" title="she4: god of the soil and altars to him;